        Your success is our priority. Start exploring and make the most of your <span class="highlight">academic potential</span>!
      </p>
      
      <div class="footer">
        <p style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-weight: 600;">
          MOUAU ClassMate Team
        </p>
        <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 12px; opacity: 0.9;">
